{"tha-ap412:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap412:0.2":"Metteyyavagga ","tha-ap412:0.3":"Udenattheraapadana ","tha-ap412:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap412:1.2":"padumo nama pabbato; ","tha-ap412:1.3":"Assamo sukato mayham, ","tha-ap412:1.4":"pannasala sumapita. ","tha-ap412:2.1":"Nadiyo sandare tattha, ","tha-ap412:2.2":"supatittha manorama; ","tha-ap412:2.3":"Acchodaka sitajala, ","tha-ap412:2.4":"sandare nadiyo sada. ","tha-ap412:3.1":"Pathina pavusa maccha, ","tha-ap412:3.2":"balaja munjarohita; ","tha-ap412:3.3":"Sobhenta nadiyo ete, ","tha-ap412:3.4":"vasanti nadiya sada. ","tha-ap412:4.1":"Ambajambuhi sanchanna, ","tha-ap412:4.2":"kareritilaka tatha; ","tha-ap412:4.3":"Uddalaka pataliyo, ","tha-ap412:4.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:5.1":"Ankolaka bimbijala, ","tha-ap412:5.2":"mayakari ca pupphita; ","tha-ap412:5.3":"Gandhena upavayanta, ","tha-ap412:5.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:6.1":"Atimutta sattalika, ","tha-ap412:6.2":"naga sala ca pupphita; ","tha-ap412:6.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap412:6.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:7.1":"Kosamba salala nipa, ","tha-ap412:7.2":"atthangapi ca pupphita; ","tha-ap412:7.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap412:7.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:8.1":"Haritaka amalaka, ","tha-ap412:8.2":"ambajambuvibhitaka; ","tha-ap412:8.3":"Kola bhallataka billa, ","tha-ap412:8.4":"phalani bahu assame. ","tha-ap412:9.1":"Kalamba kandali tattha, ","tha-ap412:9.2":"pupphanti mama assame; ","tha-ap412:9.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap412:9.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:10.1":"Asokapindivari ca, ","tha-ap412:10.2":"nimbarukkha ca pupphita; ","tha-ap412:10.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap412:10.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:11.1":"Punnaga giripunnaga, ","tha-ap412:11.2":"timira tattha pupphita; ","tha-ap412:11.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap412:11.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:12.1":"Niggundi siriniggundi, ","tha-ap412:12.2":"camparukkhettha pupphita; ","tha-ap412:12.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap412:12.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:13.1":"Avidure pokkharani, ","tha-ap412:13.2":"cakkavakupakujita; ","tha-ap412:13.3":"Mandalakehi sanchanna, ","tha-ap412:13.4":"padumuppalakehi ca. ","tha-ap412:14.1":"Acchodaka sitajala, ","tha-ap412:14.2":"supatittha manorama; ","tha-ap412:14.3":"Accha phalikasamana, ","tha-ap412:14.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:15.1":"Paduma pupphare tattha, ","tha-ap412:15.2":"pundarika ca uppala; ","tha-ap412:15.3":"Mandalakehi sanchanna, ","tha-ap412:15.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:16.1":"Pathina pavusa maccha, ","tha-ap412:16.2":"balaja munjarohita; ","tha-ap412:16.3":"Vicarantava te tattha, ","tha-ap412:16.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:17.1":"Kumbhila susumara ca, ","tha-ap412:17.2":"kacchapa ca gaha bahu; ","tha-ap412:17.3":"Ogaha ajagara ca, ","tha-ap412:17.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:18.1":"Parevata ravihamsa, ","tha-ap412:18.2":"cakkavaka nadicara; ","tha-ap412:18.3":"Dindibha salika cettha, ","tha-ap412:18.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:19.1":"Nayita ambagandhi ca, ","tha-ap412:19.2":"ketaka tattha pupphita; ","tha-ap412:19.3":"Dibbagandham sampavanta, ","tha-ap412:19.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:20.1":"Siha byaggha ca dipi ca, ","tha-ap412:20.2":"acchakokataracchaka; ","tha-ap412:20.3":"Anusancaranta pavane, ","tha-ap412:20.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:21.1":"Jatabharena bharita, ","tha-ap412:21.2":"ajinuttaravasana; ","tha-ap412:21.3":"Anusancaranta pavane, ","tha-ap412:21.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:22.1":"Ajinanidhara ete, ","tha-ap412:22.2":"nipaka santavuttino; ","tha-ap412:22.3":"Appaharava te sabbe, ","tha-ap412:22.4":"sobhenti mama assamam. ","tha-ap412:23.1":"Kharibharam gahetvana, ","tha-ap412:23.2":"ajjhogayha vanam tada; ","tha-ap412:23.3":"Mulaphalani bhunjanta, ","tha-ap412:23.4":"vasanti assame tada. ","tha-ap412:24.1":"Na te darum aharanti, ","tha-ap412:24.2":"udakam padadhovanam; ","tha-ap412:24.3":"Sabbesam anubhavena, ","tha-ap412:24.4":"sayamevahariyati. ","tha-ap412:25.1":"Cullasitisahassani, ","tha-ap412:25.2":"isayettha samagata; ","tha-ap412:25.3":"Sabbeva jhayino ete, ","tha-ap412:25.4":"uttamatthagavesaka. ","tha-ap412:26.1":"Tapassino brahmacari, ","tha-ap412:26.2":"codenta appanava te; ","tha-ap412:26.3":"Ambaravacara sabbe, ","tha-ap412:26.4":"vasanti assame tada. ","tha-ap412:27.1":"Pancaham sannipatanti, ","tha-ap412:27.2":"ekagga santavuttino; ","tha-ap412:27.3":"Annonnam abhivadetva, ","tha-ap412:27.4":"pakkamanti disamukha. ","tha-ap412:28.1":"Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap412:28.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap412:28.3":"Tamandhakaram vidhamam, ","tha-ap412:28.4":"uppajji tavade jino. ","tha-ap412:29.1":"Mama assamasamanta, ","tha-ap412:29.2":"yakkho asi mahiddhiko; ","tha-ap412:29.3":"So me samsittha sambuddham, ","tha-ap412:29.4":"jalajuttamanayakam. ","tha-ap412:30.1":"‘Esa buddho samuppanno, ","tha-ap412:30.2":"Padumuttaro mahamuni; ","tha-ap412:30.3":"Khippam gantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap412:30.4":"Payirupasa marisa’. ","tha-ap412:31.1":"Yakkhassa vacanam sutva, ","tha-ap412:31.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","tha-ap412:31.3":"Assamam samsametvana, ","tha-ap412:31.4":"nikkhamim vipina tada. ","tha-ap412:32.1":"Celeva dayhamanamhi, ","tha-ap412:32.2":"nikkhamitvana assama; ","tha-ap412:32.3":"Ekarattim nivasetva, ","tha-ap412:32.4":"upagacchim vinayakam. ","tha-ap412:33.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap412:33.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap412:33.3":"Catusaccam pakasento, ","tha-ap412:33.4":"desesi amatam padam. ","tha-ap412:34.1":"Suphullam padumam gayha, ","tha-ap412:34.2":"upagantva mahesino; ","tha-ap412:34.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap412:34.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap412:35.1":"Pujayitvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap412:35.2":"jalajuttamanayakam; ","tha-ap412:35.3":"Ekamsam ajinam katva, ","tha-ap412:35.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap412:36.1":"‘Yena nanena sambuddho, ","tha-ap412:36.2":"vasatiha anasavo; ","tha-ap412:36.3":"Tam nanam kittayissami, ","tha-ap412:36.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap412:37.1":"Samsarasotam chinditva, ","tha-ap412:37.2":"taresi sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap412:37.3":"Tava dhammam sunitvana, ","tha-ap412:37.4":"tanhasotam taranti te. ","tha-ap412:38.1":"Tuvam sattha ca ketu ca, ","tha-ap412:38.2":"dhajo yupo ca paninam; ","tha-ap412:38.3":"Parayano patittha ca, ","tha-ap412:38.4":"dipo ca dvipaduttama. ","tha-ap412:39.1":"Yavata ganino loke, ","tha-ap412:39.2":"satthavaha pavuccare; ","tha-ap412:39.3":"Tuvam aggosi sabbannu, ","tha-ap412:39.4":"tava antogadhava te. ","tha-ap412:40.1":"Tava nanena sabbannu, ","tha-ap412:40.2":"taresi janatam bahum; ","tha-ap412:40.3":"Tava dassanamagamma, ","tha-ap412:40.4":"dukkhassantam karissare. ","tha-ap412:41.1":"Ye kecime gandhajata, ","tha-ap412:41.2":"loke vayanti cakkhuma; ","tha-ap412:41.3":"Tava gandhasamo natthi, ","tha-ap412:41.4":"punnakkhette mahamune. ","tha-ap412:42.1":"Tiracchanayonim nirayam, ","tha-ap412:42.2":"parimocesi cakkhuma; ","tha-ap412:42.3":"Asankhatam padam santam, ","tha-ap412:42.4":"desesi tvam mahamune’. ","tha-ap412:43.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap412:43.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap412:43.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap412:43.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap412:44.1":"‘Yo me nanam apujesi, ","tha-ap412:44.2":"pasanno sehi panibhi; ","tha-ap412:44.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap412:44.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap412:45.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap412:45.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap412:45.3":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap412:45.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati’. ","tha-ap412:46.1":"Suladdhalabham laddhomhi, ","tha-ap412:46.2":"tosayitvana subbatam; ","tha-ap412:46.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap412:46.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap412:47.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap412:47.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap412:47.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap412:48.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap412:48.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap412:48.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap412:49.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap412:49.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap412:49.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap412:50.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma udeno thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap412:51.1":"Udenattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap412:52.1":"Metteyyavaggo ekacattalisamo. ","tha-ap412:53.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap412:54.1":"Metteyyo punnako thero, ","tha-ap412:54.2":"mettagu dhotakopi ca; ","tha-ap412:54.3":"Upasivo ca nando ca, ","tha-ap412:54.4":"hemako sattamo tahim. ","tha-ap412:55.1":"Todeyyo jatukanni ca, ","tha-ap412:55.2":"udeno ca mahayaso; ","tha-ap412:55.3":"Tini gathasatanettha, ","tha-ap412:55.4":"asiti tini cuttarim. "}